{
  "texts": [
    "Segment 4 had 13 crashes in 2023, with analysis performed on 11 crashes that had accompanying traffic data (Figure 11).",
    "Crashes involving commercial vehicles occur more frequently compared to other segments and tend to result in severe injuries.",
    "These crashes are often linked to driver fatigue or distraction (14, 63).",
    "The segment is located in a suburban area and features a straight road, which can lead to a monotonous driving environment.",
    "This monotonous setting can cause drivers to lose focus and become fatigued, increasing the risk of crashes."
  ]
}